#HELPS
-1 rules_clan~
Here are the rules for clans.  More may be added:

`&1a. `7You may only have `^one `7clanned character at one time.
This includes RP and PK clans.  Failure to follow the rule may get you
slain and unclanned.

`&1b.  `!PK `7clan leaders may not have any other `!PK `7alts.   They
may have non-pk, however.

`&1c.  `7Shared characters cannot be clanned.

`&2.  `7Clan members are not to be killing eachother.  Those that do
will be declanned and slain.

`&3.  `7Clan halls and clan equipment are for current clan members
`&ONLY`7.  If you are in a clan hall and do not belong, you will be told
to leave.  If you are caught with clan equipment and are not supposed to
have it, it will be taken away.

`&4.  `7Clan members must be active.  At least once every other week to
prevent being declanned without their knowledge.


More will be `&added `7later...~

