#12101
Entrance to the Suzaku Shrine~
Standing in front of you is the shrine of Suzaku, the Phoenix god.
A golden colored roof covers the building, curving outward at the
corners. An overhang from the shrine keeps you from getting rained on.
The walls have a simple spiral pattern on each of the panels.  The door
leading inside is to the west.
~
